<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN358-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai - atu; tuṟai - maṉaiyaṟam tuṟavaṟam. vāṉmīkiyār
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div> 
    <div xml:id="PN358">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>paruti cūḻntavip payaṅkeḻu mānila</l>
<l>morupaka leḻuva reyti yaṟṟē</l>
<l>vaiyamun tavamun tūkkiṟ ṟavattuk</l>
<l>kaiyavi yaṉaittu māṟṟā tākaliṟ</l>
<l>kaiviṭ ṭaṉarē kātala rataṉāl</l>
<l>viṭṭōrai viṭāa ṭiruvē</l>
<l>viṭāa tōrivaḷ viṭappaṭ ṭōrē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>This fertile big earth surrounded by the disk</l>
<l>is of the kind reached in one day by seven people.</l>
<l>If one weighs the world and the penance, because</l>
<l>for penance nothing changes to the extent of a mustard seed,</l>
<l>lovers do let go. Therefore,</l>
<l>Śrī does not let go of those who let go.</l>
<l>Those who do not let go are those that will get let go by her.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
